Hello, my name is Ashley and I love cars.  Even from an early age I remember having an infatuation with cars and trucks.  This has pushed me into owning a small business servicing and repairing vehicles.  

I have extensive background in mechanics and transportation giving me and understanding of fleet maintenance and logistics.  

I recently purchased a Mini Cooper and listed it on this platform.  It is probably one of the most enjoyable cars to drive.  Its compact with a big interior, all wheel drive, and will get up and go!

I enjoy traveling and renting vehicles through Turo.  I will never go back to renting through a car rental company.  The Turo community is great and I'm happy to be part of it.  Let me help you enjoy the benefits of renting through Turo!
